  "status": "Stagnant",
  "summary": "This standard introduces a smart contract interface that can represent a batch of non-fungible tokens of which the ordering information shall be retained and managed. Such information is particularly useful if `tokenId`s are encoded with the sets of `unicodes` for logographic characters and emojis. As a result, NFTs can be utilized as carriers of meanings.",
  "title": "Ordered NFT Batch Standard"
